{"comments":"HSLA color molecule - HSL with alpha transparency.\n\nHSLA extends HSL with an opacity channel, allowing for transparent colors\nin the cylindrical color space.\n\n- **Hue**: Position on the color wheel (0-359°)\n- **Saturation**: Color intensity/purity (0-100%)\n- **Lightness**: Light/dark level (0-100%)\n- **Alpha**: Opacity (0-100%): 0% = transparent, 100% = opaque\n\nLike HSL, this space is intuitive for color manipulation while supporting\ntransparency for UI effects, overlays, and compositing.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HSLA"],"HSLA"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/HSLA.purs","start":[84,1]},"title":"eqHSLA"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HSLA"],"HSLA"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[85,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/HSLA.purs","start":[85,1]},"title":"ordHSLA"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HSLA"],"HSLA"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[88,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/HSLA.purs","start":[87,1]},"title":"showHSLA"}],"comments":"HSLA color value — HSL with an alpha channel.\n\nAlpha is an Opacity (0-100%): 0% = fully transparent, 100% = fully opaque.\nThis matches the pattern of other percentage-based atoms i